  "body": "We seem to have left Quorum out of our design and test for Truffle v5. Let's use this issue as an Epic to account for the work necessary to make Truffle work with Quorum again. \r\n\r\nTo be clear, the goal of this issue is full support in Truffle for Quorum. This may include adopting/utilizing/integrating features of Quorum which weren't adequately integrated in prior Truffle versions. As always our goal is to make support as out of the box as possible, but for the sake of pragmatism minimal user-initiated configuration steps, installation of extra dependencies, or other similar tasks are fine, provided they are straightforward. That said, any user-initiated steps required for full Quorum support should be addressed in our user docs on our website before this issue should be considered resolved.\r\n\r\nIssues in this epic (for non-zenhub users):\r\n\r\n- [x] [Accommodate broken support for Quorum/other chains via `--legacy` flags to use old code](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/1543) - **Available in [v5.0.9](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v5.0.9)**\r\n- [x] [`truffle migrate` on private permissioned Quorum network returns nothing to console](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/1622) - **Available in [v5.0.9](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v5.0.9)**\r\n- [x] [Add support for Quorum's privateFor transaction parameter](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/1656) - **Available in [v5.0.14](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v5.0.14)**\r\n- [ ] [Add support for signing Quorum private transactions](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/2153)\n- [ ] [Audit Truffle's existing features/APIs for compatibility with/exposure of Quorum's feature set](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/1658)\r\n",
